        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=83005&amp;TOPIC_ID=9414&amp;FORUM_ID=13&amp;CAT_ID=2&amp;Forum_Title=Newbie+Land&amp;Topic_Title=bunch+of+newbie+questions&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         <ul><li><font color=green>1.</font id=green> DEFINITELY do not put points into STA. At level 54 I can tell you that if I had invested 5 points in STA it would have netted me 11HP - 2HP per STA is just not worth it.</P><P>Max your INT (unless perhaps you are an Erudite :)</P><P>If you want to re-roll then consider putting your points into Strength - as a soloer you will find that you are often encumbered with loot - every little bit of strength helps.</P><P>Personally I wouldn't bother - keep your stats as they are.</li></P><P><li><font color=green>2.</font id=green> I'd pretty much agree with Leslee</li></P><P><li><font color=green>3.</font id=green> Always look for bargains. You will not be able to afford everything you want for a long time, so where you see something that can be resold at a higher value then go for it. I'm not saying buy spells cheap and gouge your brother necro's, but certainly try to maximise your profit.</li></P><P><li><font color=green>4.</font id=green> AFAIK pets are affected by level requirements just as we are. Look at the Games guide/FAQ for details of pet levels.</li></P><P><li><font color=green>5.</font id=green> I'm sure that Deity based Necro items exist, but I have yet to come across one. If nobody provides information to the contrary then assume that this is not something to worry about.</li></P><P><li><font color=green>6.</font id=green> Depends on your play style. Look at the spells covered by each class and decide which you will be using most. Most players decide alteration, but it doesn't mean that's the right choice for you.</li></ul></P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=236573" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.clement-evans.co.uk/xatan/xatan-eyes-heretic.jpg" border=0></a><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

    </table></td>
  </tr>
